.slack 
  .section1.relative(style="background-color:#00adef; height:250px;")
    .container(style="color:white;")
      .row
        .col-xs-9.col-xs-offset-2
          %div{:style => "height:25px;"}
          %div.hidden-lg.hidden-md.hidden-sm{:style => "height: 75px;"}
          %img.hidden-xs.hidden-sm.hidden-md{:src => "/images/slack-logo5.png", :style => "height:100px; width:100px; margin-left: 25px; "}
          %img.hidden-xs.hidden-md.hidden-lg{:src => "/images/slack-logo5.png", :style => "height:100px; width:100px; margin-left: -100px;"}
          %img.hidden-xs.hidden-sm.hidden-lg{:src => "/images/slack-logo5.png", :style => "height:100px; width:100px; margin-left: -50px;"}

          %h1{:style => "color:white;  font-family: 'AvantGarde-Demi',  sans-serif; font-size: 60px; text-align:center;  margin-top: -90px "} Count.It for Slack
          %h3{:style => "color: #555555; font-weight: 100; color:white; font-size: 21px; text-align:center; margin-top: -2px;"}Broadcasting motivation to your Slack channels.
          %div(style="height:25px;")  
  .section2
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          %div()     
            .title
            %p
              Count.It hosts physical activity challenges for teams, and now you can bring all that action into your Slack @channels.
          
              Connect tracking apps/devices, get live notifications, check out the leaderboard, right from Slack.

        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          %div()     
        
          %div()
            .title Meet the CountItBot 
            %p
              Like a sportscaster, the CountItBot reports status of your Count.It challenge to a specified Slack Channel.  CountItBot lets you know about lead changes and other other challenge action to help keep wellness on your radar.
              
          %div()
            .title  Count It on Slack
            %ul
              %li 
                %span.bold
                  \/countit me
                %br.hidden-sm.hidden-lg.hidden-md
                to check your current score, rank and connected trackers.
              %li 
                %span.bold
                  \/countit (group, metro or world)
                %br.hidden-sm.hidden-lg.hidden-md
                to check the leaderboards.
              %li 
                %span.bold
                  \/countit rewards
                %br.hidden-sm.hidden-lg.hidden-md
                to check rewards available to you. 
          
          %div()
            .title Login with Slack
            %p
              Don't worry about entering your email or remembering a separate password for Count.It just log in with Slack.
              
          %div()
            .title Public or Private
            %p
              Count.It allows groups to battle each other on public metro area and national leaderboards.  Groups can opt in/out of public competition, by setting the privacy option in their Group Settings. (Default is Private) 

          %div()
            .title Support
            %p
              Please email any questions to info@countit.com , or click on the light bulb at the bottom right corner of our site to provide feedback.

        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          %div(style="height:25px;")  
          %div(style="text-align:center; padding-top:25px;")
            %img(src="/images/bot-circle.png" style="display:inline;")
            %h2(style="display:inline; color:#00adef; padding-left: 10px; padding-bottom:10px;vertical-align:middle;") Get CountItBot for Free
            %br
            %br
            %a{:href => "/auth/slack"}
              %img(src="/images/add_to_slack.png" style="height:50px;" ) 

          
